Package gov.nasa.arc.mct.gui

Provides the interfaces and classes defining the MCT GUI interactions for MCT components.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ActionContext This interface defines the context information passed to a ContextAwareAction.
CompositeViewManifestationProvider An interface to mark an object which can provide multiple manifestations.
FeedView.DataTransformation This interface defines an arbitrary transformation on a set of feed data.
FeedView.RenderingCallback This interface defines an arbitrary operation performed on set of feed data.
FeedView.SynchronizationControl Provide interaction with the synchronization time state.
MCTViewManifestationInfo Defines the UI rendering info used in persistence of composed views.
NamingContext This interface defines the concept of a naming context.
SelectionProvider This specifies the interface for widgets that contribute to the selection model.
TableHolderManifestation Defines an object to hold a reference to a table widget.
TwiddleView This interface defines the methods that a view must provide to be twiddle-able.
ViewListener Defines an event sent when there is interaction between a view manifestation and the directory tree or a dropped object.
ViewProvider Defines a provider of view manifestations.
 

Class Summary
AbstractViewListener A skeleton implementation of ViewListener.
ActionContextImpl This class defines a context for executing actions.
ActionManager This class manages the actions in MCT.
CompositeAction This class defines a composite action, which will be swapped during runtime by a set of actions that are dynamically populated.
ContextAwareAction This class defines the super class for actions used in MCT.
ContextAwareMenu This class defines the super class for menus used in MCT.
FeedManagerImpl Provides an instance of a FeedManager.
FeedView This is the super class for feed displays.
FileChooser Implements a file chooser for which the user can control the modality, application-modal or document-modal.
FrameUtil Implements utility methods for finding information about frames that have been created.
GroupAction This class defines an action for a menu item group.
GroupAction.RadioAction This abstract class defines the action contained in a GroupAction.
HidableTabbedPane A tabbed pane that hides the tabs when there is only one tab.
MCTFlipFlopAction Action for toggle commands.
MCTGUIResourceBundle This class contains the static GUI constants.
MCTMutableTreeNode A DefaultMutableTreeNode which contains a flag to indicate if a node is just a proxy to its children or actually contains real children.
MCTSplitPaneFactory Implements a factory that creates arbitrarily nested split panes.
MCTViewManifestationInfoImpl Implements the rendering information used in the persistence of composed views.
MenuExtensionManager Implements a manager of extended menu items.
MenuItemInfo This class consists of the information necessary for creating a menu item in MCT.
MenuSection Contains a list of MenuItemInfo instances.
OptionBox Implements static methods to show dialog boxes to show messages or get user input.
Request This class defines a time span.
RowSize Row size stored as a key-value pair.
SplittablePane A pane that can be split into two parts or not.
StatusAreaWidgetRegistryImpl Provides the implementation of StatusAreaWidgetRegistry.
Twistie This class implements the twistie.
View Implements a skeleton of a view.
ViewRoleSelection This class implements the transferrable class consisting of an array of ViewRole objects.
WindowManagerImpl Implements a window manager.
 

Enum Summary
MenuItemInfo.MenuItemType MCT-supported menu item types.
